{
  "stem": "3685.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And somebody came in through the door, so I'll run in the back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Laid down, I couldn't fall asleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And finally I said, I'm going there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Came in to the Kranc's-- his, the father, the-- one daughter, the future husband, and that-- your little Josi, 10 years, they were sitting and looking on pictures.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew the house very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I opened the oven.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I knew there's something there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I took out-- it either was a duck or a chicken.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, I was so hungry, I just couldn't-- and I ate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then Kranc says, let's go and look at the-- at, at-- I want to see my family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were all laying down there, not buried, shot in the back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So after-- and it start getting early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Kranc said, Max, I have a place where to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't take you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I says, I know where you're going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's my last word.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's my last time I see him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I say, I don't want to go to that place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was right, because they found them there, murdered, all choked they were with a wire-- him, and his daughter, and the son, and the, and the future, and the future-- the daughter's husband.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They went to a Ukrainian family, which I knew the family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I knew they were friends before the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then, when we were hiding already, this particular family was-- which hid us came over one morning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they told us-- and he told us that they found the Krances all dead on a field.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He killed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He killed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, when he told me that, because is going there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
